WEBVTT

01:40.470 --> 01:45.910
[Speed and Love]

01:46.270 --> 01:48.820
[Episode 1]

02:06.790 --> 02:07.480
Mumu.

02:08.280 --> 02:08.880
Look.

02:09.199 --> 02:11.150
You look so elegant in this outfit.

02:11.320 --> 02:12.150
So beautiful.

02:12.830 --> 02:14.760
We've already prepared your room.

02:15.760 --> 02:16.760
It's on the fourth floor.

02:16.760 --> 02:17.960
I'm not staying here.

02:18.079 --> 02:19.610
I want to live in my own home.

02:20.760 --> 02:22.220
He's not my father either.

02:23.200 --> 02:24.870
He's just your new husband.

02:27.200 --> 02:27.800
Mumu.

02:27.920 --> 02:29.450
Don't be so stubborn, okay?

02:31.480 --> 02:33.990
Don't think I don't know
what you're thinking.

02:33.990 --> 02:35.200
You refuse to move out

02:35.530 --> 02:37.040
because you think Jin Zhao and your father

02:37.040 --> 02:38.370
would come back for you.

02:39.480 --> 02:40.880
You're not a kid anymore.

02:41.200 --> 02:43.200
How can you still be so naive?

02:44.870 --> 02:45.990
He promised me

02:46.610 --> 02:48.550
he would definitely come back to see me.

02:48.550 --> 02:49.240
He?

02:49.870 --> 02:50.550
Who?

02:54.200 --> 02:55.200
Jin Zhao?

02:55.590 --> 02:56.240
Mumu.

02:56.920 --> 02:58.520
I forgot to tell you something

02:58.520 --> 02:59.710
about Jin Zhao.

03:01.270 --> 03:03.520
The reason
he hasn't been in touch for years

03:03.520 --> 03:04.640
is because he doesn't have

03:04.640 --> 03:06.080
any decent job there.

03:07.110 --> 03:08.360
He's not your brother,

03:08.360 --> 03:09.820
and you're not his sister.

03:10.270 --> 03:12.670
Your father
also has his own new family now.

03:12.960 --> 03:14.800
You're not family anymore.

03:16.390 --> 03:18.590
So don't have too much contact with them

03:18.800 --> 03:20.040
It's no good for you.

03:38.670 --> 03:39.320
Thank you.

03:39.430 --> 03:40.270
I'm Nana.

03:42.360 --> 03:43.040
I'm Jiang Mu.

03:43.040 --> 03:44.520
Hello, hello.

03:45.550 --> 03:47.350
Are you going there for tourism?

03:48.390 --> 03:49.790
I'm looking for someone.

03:50.270 --> 03:52.200
He's been in Manshi for many years.

03:53.110 --> 03:55.360
A reunion after a long separation?

03:55.990 --> 03:57.550
What kind of person is he?

03:58.079 --> 03:58.960
Well, he...

04:00.240 --> 04:01.500
had excellent grades.

04:01.670 --> 04:03.200
The walls at home

04:03.320 --> 04:04.980
were covered with his awards.

04:05.520 --> 04:08.240
His knowledge emits elegance.

04:08.760 --> 04:10.220
He has a great personality

04:10.480 --> 04:11.540
and is very gentle.

04:11.920 --> 04:13.800
He never loses his temper with me.

04:16.120 --> 04:17.680
His fingers are beautiful;

04:18.560 --> 04:19.829
slender and fair,

04:20.269 --> 04:21.930
with well-defined knuckles.

04:23.080 --> 04:23.880
You know what?

04:24.150 --> 04:25.880
He has beautiful handwriting.

04:29.230 --> 04:30.390
What does he look like?

04:30.390 --> 04:31.720
Is he the handsome type?

04:33.120 --> 04:34.080
This is for you.

04:34.830 --> 04:35.960
When I come back,

04:36.320 --> 04:38.250
I'll check how your handwriting's

04:38.680 --> 04:39.880
coming along.

04:45.060 --> 04:47.210
I haven't seen him for a long time.

04:52.790 --> 05:01.470
[Manshi Underground Boxing Club]

06:12.080 --> 06:13.270
Jin Qiang, it's me.

06:13.760 --> 06:15.360
Jiang Mu has gone to find you.

06:15.760 --> 06:16.790
Go pick her up at the airport.

06:16.790 --> 06:18.230
Don't let Jin Zhao
get in contact with her.

06:18.230 --> 06:19.560
Bring her back quickly.

06:20.560 --> 06:21.620
Are you listening?

06:21.950 --> 06:23.280
Go pick her up yourself.

06:36.150 --> 06:37.790
Go pick someone up for me.

06:40.350 --> 06:41.120
Who?

06:41.880 --> 06:43.030
Your sister.

06:47.720 --> 06:48.480
Sister?

06:48.830 --> 06:50.630
I'll send you the details later.

06:54.650 --> 06:56.050
I might as well get drunk.

06:59.420 --> 07:02.030
[Pick up someone from the airport.
Their flight's FD569.]

07:40.230 --> 07:41.630
Terminal 1, first floor,

07:41.909 --> 07:43.390
left exit, gate number 8.

07:48.710 --> 07:50.270
How's it going, bro?

07:52.710 --> 07:54.970
Do you want to go
to this store or that one?

07:55.390 --> 07:57.030
Let's ask that person.

07:58.610 --> 07:59.370
Excuse me.

07:59.560 --> 08:01.760
I want to go to this store.

08:01.780 --> 08:02.470
I'm sorry.

08:02.500 --> 08:03.200
Could you help me check

08:03.200 --> 08:05.440
how to get to this place?

08:05.460 --> 08:06.390
Don't touch her!

08:42.460 --> 08:43.789
Don't you recognize me?

08:58.160 --> 08:59.960
Jin Qiang asked me to pick you up.

09:30.110 --> 09:31.470
What are you standing there for?

09:31.470 --> 09:32.160
Get in.

09:45.160 --> 09:46.420
Fasten your seatbelt.

10:34.350 --> 10:35.750
Why are you staring at me?

10:40.630 --> 10:41.510
Are you hot?

10:43.960 --> 10:44.920
No.

10:58.830 --> 10:59.800
Is this car

11:00.630 --> 11:01.630
yours?

11:02.080 --> 11:02.750
No,

11:03.280 --> 11:04.080
I borrowed it.

11:06.680 --> 11:08.010
Are you still in school?

11:09.500 --> 11:10.220
No.

11:13.830 --> 11:16.080
Did you just graduate or...

11:16.510 --> 11:17.910
I quit after high school.

11:18.040 --> 11:20.100
But you used to have such good grades.

11:20.590 --> 11:22.390
You were always top of the class.

11:22.990 --> 11:24.120
You even promised me

11:24.400 --> 11:26.000
you'd get a master's degree.

11:34.320 --> 11:35.160
Get lost.

11:36.160 --> 11:37.760
Come out for drinks tonight.

11:38.440 --> 11:39.110
Nope.

11:39.590 --> 11:40.630
Who's that chick?

11:41.350 --> 11:43.810
Better watch out
or Snakey will make a scene.

11:57.800 --> 11:59.130
Was that person just now

11:59.870 --> 12:00.960
your friend?

12:03.080 --> 12:05.410
Why are you friends with people like this?

12:11.680 --> 12:12.440
One, please.

12:12.700 --> 12:13.430
Okay.

12:21.090 --> 12:22.710
[Brother]

12:26.400 --> 12:27.750
How did he suddenly

12:28.680 --> 12:29.710
get so tall?

12:32.040 --> 12:33.280
And his friends

12:33.710 --> 12:35.840
don't look like decent people either.

12:37.110 --> 12:38.920
There's blood on him too.

12:41.230 --> 12:42.160
All these years,

12:43.350 --> 12:45.350
what kind of life has he been living?

12:50.030 --> 12:51.730
[Jin Zhao]

13:08.440 --> 13:09.160
Thank you.

13:25.400 --> 13:26.230
Run, Zhao!

13:26.830 --> 13:27.930
Run! Run!

13:27.960 --> 13:28.510
Okay.

13:28.920 --> 13:29.990
Don't get caught!

13:30.280 --> 13:31.230
Okay.
Let’s go home.

13:31.230 --> 13:32.630
let's wash the strawberries.

13:32.630 --> 13:33.440
Let's eat them

13:33.470 --> 13:34.350
while they're sweet.

13:34.350 --> 13:34.960
Okay!

13:38.560 --> 13:39.220
Is it sweet?

13:39.630 --> 13:40.440
Yeah.

13:40.800 --> 13:42.040
But not the back part.

13:43.290 --> 13:45.220
Give me the ones that aren't sweet.

13:51.280 --> 13:52.410
He still remembers.

14:12.320 --> 14:13.180
It's upstairs.

14:13.320 --> 14:14.080
Follow me.

15:05.350 --> 15:06.880
Just a few flights of stairs

15:07.230 --> 15:09.040
and you're already out of breath?

15:09.040 --> 15:09.920
Yeah,

15:12.110 --> 15:13.630
You need to get fitter.

15:14.400 --> 15:17.260
How come you're not panting
after all those stairs?

15:17.590 --> 15:18.520
I'm used to this.

15:50.500 --> 15:51.260
Wake up.

15:51.830 --> 15:53.090
I've brought her here.

15:57.110 --> 15:57.970
Where's my dad?

16:08.280 --> 16:08.990
That's him.

16:11.080 --> 16:13.200
Get up and wash your face.
It's covered in blood.

16:13.200 --> 16:14.060
What happened?

16:15.040 --> 16:16.160
Covered in blood?

16:17.750 --> 16:18.870
I'll go myself.

16:22.920 --> 16:23.870
Don't mind him.

16:24.230 --> 16:25.710
All he does is drink all day long.

16:25.710 --> 16:27.230
He'll drink himself sick sooner or later.

16:27.230 --> 16:28.040
If he doesn't end up with liver cancer,

16:28.040 --> 16:29.440
I'll count my blessings.

16:29.920 --> 16:30.590
Zhao,

16:31.040 --> 16:32.640
come help me make dumplings.

16:36.230 --> 16:37.280
You must be...

16:37.680 --> 16:38.560
Mumu.

16:41.080 --> 16:42.200
You're so tall,

16:42.510 --> 16:44.320
and even prettier than in your photos.

16:44.320 --> 16:45.160
Come rest up.

16:46.750 --> 16:48.230
I made dumplings for you.

16:48.470 --> 16:49.730
They'll be ready soon.

16:50.510 --> 16:51.040
Thank you.

16:51.040 --> 16:52.200
You're so pretty.

16:52.510 --> 16:54.910
Good thing
you don't look like your father.

16:55.300 --> 16:57.360
My dad was handsome when he was young.

16:57.400 --> 16:58.160
Is that so?

16:58.280 --> 17:00.410
Well, I never saw him when he was young.

17:02.710 --> 17:03.960
Did you put salt in the dumpling filling?

17:03.960 --> 17:05.030
I don't think I did.

17:07.030 --> 17:07.990
You added soy sauce, right?

17:07.990 --> 17:08.599
Yes.

17:08.880 --> 17:10.310
I put in half a bottle of soy sauce.

17:10.310 --> 17:11.710
Then why would you add salt?

17:11.710 --> 17:12.640
Gah! Jin Qiang drives me crazy

17:12.640 --> 17:14.119
every single day!

17:20.069 --> 17:21.880
Xin, say hello to your sister.

17:23.430 --> 17:24.750
Xin, I'm talking to you.

17:24.750 --> 17:25.599
Greet her.

17:26.060 --> 17:26.859
How rude!

17:27.880 --> 17:28.680
It's okay.

17:29.400 --> 17:30.530
She doesn't have to.

17:31.070 --> 17:32.680
It's our first meeting after all.

17:32.680 --> 17:34.640
She should still greet you
even if it's the first meeting.

17:34.640 --> 17:35.440
You two

17:35.600 --> 17:37.400
are blood-related sisters.

17:52.680 --> 17:53.410
Say hello.

17:57.880 --> 17:58.710
Sister.

18:02.370 --> 18:03.050
Come.

18:07.680 --> 18:09.210
I brought gifts for you all.

18:09.360 --> 18:10.840
We're all family.

18:11.200 --> 18:12.990
Why spend this money?

18:14.160 --> 18:16.160
Look how well-raised this child is,

18:16.470 --> 18:18.680
polite and beautiful.

18:32.600 --> 18:33.640
I didn't add any fillers today.

18:33.640 --> 18:34.790
It's all pure meat.

18:39.320 --> 18:41.210
Why does she get more than me?

18:44.270 --> 18:45.120
She's a guest.

18:59.990 --> 19:01.400
Isn't this filling

19:02.840 --> 19:03.990
a bit too salty?

19:05.800 --> 19:07.470
It tastes fine to me.

19:08.960 --> 19:10.270
What would you know?

19:10.750 --> 19:11.750
You drink alcohol

19:11.790 --> 19:12.990
like water every day.

19:13.030 --> 19:15.030
Your taste buds are pickled in alcohol.

19:15.030 --> 19:16.360
How can you taste anything?

19:16.360 --> 19:16.890
No wonder

19:16.920 --> 19:19.180
our restaurant is doing worse and worse.

19:20.640 --> 19:21.470
Brandy!

19:28.960 --> 19:30.030
What brings you here?

19:30.030 --> 19:32.290
Hey, Brandy, I need to ask you something.

19:32.470 --> 19:33.160
Sanlai!

19:33.270 --> 19:34.270
Have you eaten yet?

19:34.270 --> 19:34.750
Go get a bowl.

19:34.750 --> 19:36.710
Come, sit here and have a drink with me.

19:36.710 --> 19:37.710
Everyone's home?

19:40.920 --> 19:41.920
I'll pass today.

19:42.070 --> 19:43.470
Uncle, I'll drink with you next time.

19:43.470 --> 19:45.730
I need to talk to Brandy about something.

19:49.120 --> 19:49.890
You all eat first.

19:49.890 --> 19:51.350
I'll step out for a moment.

20:06.710 --> 20:08.840
Have you really thought this through?

20:09.200 --> 20:10.360
What if you die?

20:19.630 --> 20:20.500
Your relative?

20:25.790 --> 20:26.710
I'm leaving first.

20:26.710 --> 20:28.170
Think about it carefully.

20:41.270 --> 20:42.120
Young girl,

20:43.310 --> 20:44.310
my name is Sanlai.

20:44.920 --> 20:45.920
What's your name?

20:46.640 --> 20:47.470
Jiang Mu.

20:49.440 --> 20:51.370
Meaning "yearning day and night"?

20:56.880 --> 20:57.840
Jiang Mu.

20:58.640 --> 21:00.220
Come visit my shop sometime.

21:00.220 --> 21:01.480
I'll tell you a secret.

21:09.030 --> 21:09.920
Looking for me?

21:21.990 --> 21:23.190
This is a gift for you.

21:27.880 --> 21:30.270
Don't spend money
buying things for me in the future.

21:30.270 --> 21:31.530
It's still necessary.

21:32.680 --> 21:33.920
After all, I'm...

21:34.690 --> 21:35.490
a guest.

21:58.510 --> 21:59.650
What is he doing now

21:59.680 --> 22:00.880
if he's not in school?

22:01.820 --> 22:02.970
Why are there

22:03.470 --> 22:04.990
blood stains on his face?

22:05.470 --> 22:06.800
Are you sure about this?

22:07.510 --> 22:08.840
What if you die?

22:37.170 --> 22:37.650
[Zhao]

23:03.440 --> 23:04.470
Brother.

23:06.470 --> 23:08.360
You dropped something.

23:09.710 --> 23:11.990
"Yearning day and night."

23:39.270 --> 23:42.070
[Yearning day and night]

23:50.850 --> 23:53.670
[I've approved your friend request.
We can now chat.]

23:53.640 --> 23:54.600
Where are you?

23:55.400 --> 23:56.270
I'm hungry.

24:11.070 --> 24:11.880
Come down.

25:05.550 --> 25:06.610
Where are we going?

25:07.840 --> 25:08.970
Weren't you hungry?

25:10.200 --> 25:11.460
Let's get some supper.

26:06.750 --> 26:08.280
Why are you skipping about?

26:09.510 --> 26:10.990
We're going for supper.

26:11.310 --> 26:12.470
I'm just moving around a bit

26:12.470 --> 26:13.510
so I can eat more.

26:20.680 --> 26:22.410
Do you normally like drinking—

26:41.750 --> 26:42.680
You're not a kid anymore.

26:42.680 --> 26:44.810
Don't you know how to cross the street?

26:51.120 --> 26:52.180
Do you know the way?

26:53.840 --> 26:54.750
No, I don't.

27:13.270 --> 27:14.200
Watch out!

27:20.270 --> 27:21.670
Watch out for the puddle.

27:35.750 --> 27:36.560
Steamed buns?

27:45.960 --> 27:46.790
Barbecue?

27:59.230 --> 28:00.290
Pick what you want.

28:04.400 --> 28:05.710
I can choose anything?

28:07.400 --> 28:09.460
Let's go with the busiest stall then.

28:15.440 --> 28:16.190
Let's go.

28:46.540 --> 28:47.670
Seafood fried rice.

28:48.440 --> 28:49.900
Do you need anything else?

28:51.550 --> 28:52.360
This and this.

28:52.470 --> 28:53.310
Is that all?

29:17.600 --> 29:19.600
Don't you have anything to say to me?

29:21.400 --> 29:22.200
Like what?

29:22.640 --> 29:24.790
It's been a long time.

29:26.360 --> 29:27.420
Aren't you curious

29:27.640 --> 29:28.640
about my life

29:28.790 --> 29:30.120
and how I've been doing?

29:36.920 --> 29:38.250
How's your stepfather?

29:40.230 --> 29:41.200
Just so-so.

29:42.270 --> 29:43.750
So you ran away from home?

29:45.360 --> 29:46.880
Who said I ran away?

29:49.200 --> 29:50.400
Then why are you here?

29:52.270 --> 29:53.470
I'm here as a tourist.

29:54.200 --> 29:56.030
Your mom bought you a return ticket.

29:56.030 --> 29:57.290
Get some rest tonight.

29:57.400 --> 29:59.200
I'll take you to the airport tomorrow.

29:59.200 --> 30:00.260
I'm not going back.

30:00.470 --> 30:01.750
Then call your mother.

30:02.120 --> 30:02.840
Fine.

30:06.030 --> 30:07.510
I'm not going back tomorrow.

30:07.510 --> 30:08.570
Cancel the ticket.

30:11.710 --> 30:14.440
I already asked her
to cancel tomorrow's flight.

30:15.030 --> 30:15.840
Did she agree?

30:16.030 --> 30:17.030
It doesn't matter.

30:17.030 --> 30:19.290
I've already turned off my phone anyway.

30:27.030 --> 30:29.120
I heard there's a place here
with lots of young people.

30:29.120 --> 30:30.320
I want to check it out.

30:30.750 --> 30:31.950
Check it out for what?

30:32.360 --> 30:33.360
For romance.

30:41.410 --> 30:43.600
Since you're not curious about my life,

30:43.600 --> 30:44.270
why don't we

30:44.470 --> 30:45.930
talk about yours instead?

30:46.550 --> 30:47.510
How have you been

30:52.160 --> 30:53.400
all these years?

30:56.640 --> 30:57.510
Not great.

30:58.360 --> 30:59.400
Tell me more.

31:05.230 --> 31:06.630
I'll ask, and you answer.

31:08.920 --> 31:10.250
What do you want to know?

31:10.470 --> 31:11.710
What are you doing tomorrow?

31:11.710 --> 31:12.230
Work.

31:12.310 --> 31:13.310
What kind of work?

31:14.630 --> 31:15.640
What about the day after?

31:15.640 --> 31:16.900
Do you need something?

31:18.360 --> 31:19.750
Do you do anything else?

31:19.990 --> 31:20.920
Make money.

31:21.310 --> 31:22.570
Besides making money?

31:33.600 --> 31:34.400
Of course.

31:36.400 --> 31:38.860
Eat, drink, sleep,
take a dump, and have fun.

31:38.990 --> 31:40.720
Which one are you asking about?

31:41.310 --> 31:42.470
Let's talk about

31:44.710 --> 31:45.970
the "having fun" part.

31:47.160 --> 31:49.160
Are you sure you want to talk about that?

31:49.160 --> 31:49.990
Why?

31:50.640 --> 31:53.570
Not comfortable discussing it with me,
your sister?

31:54.920 --> 31:56.120
I've had too much fun,

31:56.540 --> 31:58.340
can't remember it all right now.

31:58.510 --> 32:00.240
Then let's change the subject.

32:02.750 --> 32:05.190
Tell me about your new sister.

32:12.440 --> 32:13.400
You mean Jin Xin?

32:17.840 --> 32:18.970
Why are you smiling?

32:27.470 --> 32:29.220
Bro, eating here again?

32:29.680 --> 32:30.550
New boyfriend?

32:56.400 --> 32:58.400
You're not replying to my messages.

32:58.920 --> 33:00.720
So you're here picking up girls?

33:01.030 --> 33:01.790
Brandy.

33:02.310 --> 33:04.550
You like younger ones now?

33:04.940 --> 33:07.340
Not even introducing her to your brothers?

33:07.360 --> 33:08.550
Keeping her all to yourself.

33:08.550 --> 33:09.880
Stop talking nonsense.

33:09.960 --> 33:11.090
That's not what I do.

33:11.750 --> 33:12.410
Young girl,

33:12.600 --> 33:14.000
let me introduce myself.

33:14.160 --> 33:15.270
I'm Crazy Jin.

33:22.600 --> 33:24.790
Wasn't she the girlfriend on your car?

33:27.230 --> 33:28.230
She's my...

33:29.990 --> 33:30.680
Sister.

33:31.200 --> 33:32.460
She's here traveling.

33:32.640 --> 33:33.840
Leaving in a few days.

33:34.360 --> 33:35.310
Sister?

33:35.840 --> 33:38.070
Isn't your sister in elementary school?

33:38.070 --> 33:39.870
Where did this sister come from?

33:41.120 --> 33:42.120
Are you

33:42.640 --> 33:43.640
related by blood?

33:54.200 --> 33:55.120
I heard

33:55.510 --> 33:57.040
you're going to that match.

33:57.230 --> 33:58.920
That Lin is trouble.

33:59.390 --> 34:01.050
Be careful, he might kill you.

34:08.389 --> 34:09.830
Don't just eat.

34:10.070 --> 34:11.719
Can't we just chat?

34:12.030 --> 34:12.760
Waiter!

34:12.920 --> 34:13.440
Yes?

34:13.590 --> 34:14.670
A dozen beers!

34:16.320 --> 34:17.380
Another glass too!

34:17.550 --> 34:18.280
Okay!

34:18.469 --> 34:19.550
Can you drink?

34:20.320 --> 34:21.800
I ditched that girl

34:22.030 --> 34:24.070
just to come find you
and keep you company.

34:24.070 --> 34:25.670
Your drinks.

34:25.670 --> 34:26.239
Thanks.

34:26.239 --> 34:27.719
Hello? Check, please.

34:27.880 --> 34:29.840
Okay. Just wait a moment please.

34:33.590 --> 34:35.449
Your sister is easily satisfied.

34:36.560 --> 34:37.190
You want to take care of her?

34:37.190 --> 34:37.989
Sure.

34:38.239 --> 34:40.239
Sister, hang out with me from now on.

34:40.340 --> 34:41.770
I'll make sure you eat and drink well.

34:41.770 --> 34:43.280
I'll feed you until you're plump,

34:43.280 --> 34:44.510
even prettier than now.

34:44.510 --> 34:45.280
How about it?

34:46.429 --> 34:47.889
Is she really your sister?

34:48.550 --> 34:50.070
She doesn't look like you.

34:50.880 --> 34:53.030
Be careful Snakey catches you.

34:55.280 --> 34:55.949
Let's go.

34:56.440 --> 34:58.370
Don't go! The drinks just arrived!

34:58.510 --> 34:59.110
Sister!

34:59.110 --> 35:00.510
Who is Snakey?

35:00.800 --> 35:01.400
Nobody.

35:01.510 --> 35:02.510
Your girlfriend?

35:02.810 --> 35:03.520
No.

35:07.240 --> 35:07.990
Over there!

35:10.740 --> 35:11.700
Who are they?

35:15.480 --> 35:16.190
They're all our people.

35:16.190 --> 35:17.150
Get lost.

35:19.960 --> 35:21.280
Chase him!

35:34.470 --> 35:35.150
Stay back!

35:57.440 --> 35:58.150
Brandy!

35:58.840 --> 35:59.550
Let's go.

36:54.040 --> 36:58.760
♪ Forgotten between the rearview mirror ♪

37:01.010 --> 37:07.190
♪ The heart that is still beating
hasn't said goodbye yet ♪

37:07.650 --> 37:10.920
♪ Meeting again after many years ♪

37:09.440 --> 37:11.290
I've had many dreams about us reuniting.

37:11.290 --> 37:14.200
♪ The coffee is too sour and bitter;
I'm greedy for something sweet ♪

37:12.240 --> 37:13.550
But no moment

37:14.360 --> 37:16.030
was as real as this one.

37:15.320 --> 37:17.950
♪ Who will circle around the line
bordering the thoughts? ♪

37:17.590 --> 37:19.190
Everything has changed

37:18.310 --> 37:22.440
♪ Stupidly,
I refuse to believe there's an end ♪

37:20.150 --> 37:21.880
smelling this familiar scent.

37:23.070 --> 37:23.880
But...

37:23.210 --> 37:25.200
♪ I must ♪

37:25.190 --> 37:26.590
it feels like nothing's changed too.

37:25.220 --> 37:29.040
♪ Continue to love,
between the sun and the moon ♪

37:29.060 --> 37:32.470
♪ Even in pain,
we indulge in the iron-like vows ♪

37:32.680 --> 37:34.200
♪ Willingly ♪

37:36.820 --> 37:40.040
♪ At this moment ♪

37:40.260 --> 37:43.700
♪ I run towards you
before the night falls ♪

37:43.720 --> 37:48.240
♪ Don't ask about the past;
just bet on tomorrow ♪

37:48.280 --> 37:51.450
♪ Those dreams and longings ♪

37:51.830 --> 37:56.100
♪ The trails overlap again ♪
